          <p dir="auto">Thanks James, that's why I pulled you in, I was sure there might be some issues.</p>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">My concern with this patch is that a third party lib that uses jQuery is loaded on a page with an AMD loader. This patch would mean the AMD loader would get that version of jQuery but the third party lib would not see a global jQuery object, and errors would occur.</p>
