<p dir="auto">And just before that is the part where jQuery defines itself as AMD-ready:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-js notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="if ( typeof define === &quot;function&quot; &amp;&amp; define.amd ) {
