+&lt;?php
+/*
+Plugin Name: CardConnect Payment Gateway
+Plugin URI: http://sofcorp.com/
+Description: Accept credit card payments in your WooCommerce store!
+Version: 0.0.0 Alpha
+Author: SOF Inc &lt;eran@sofcorp.com&gt;
